{
  "meta": {
    "project": "Módulo Restaurante Backend",
    "date": "2026-02-12",
    "prepared_by": "Software Development Manager"
  },
  "product_overview": "Extensión de un sistema e-commerce para soportar operaciones de restaurante, incluyendo modificadores de productos, gestión de mesas, y workflow de cocina con control de inventario.",
  "core_goals": [
    "Agregar soporte para modificadores de producto anidados en productos de tipo PHYSICAL en el sistema e-commerce.",
    "Permitir la creación, actualización y gestión de órdenes con selección de modificadores, cantidades, notas y asignación de mesa.",
    "Implementar un workflow de estado de órdenes adaptado a operaciones de restaurante incluyendo estados específicos de cocina y servicio.",
    "Garantizar integridad de stock con decremento atómico y validaciones de selección de modificadores.",
    "Mantener compatibilidad hacia atrás con productos tipo DIGITAL y operaciones existentes."
  ],
  "key_features": [
    "Creación y actualización de productos con grupos de modificadores y sus opciones, permitiendo límites de selección y ajustes de precio.",
    "Modelo extendido en base de datos Prisma con nuevas entidades ModifierGroup, Modifier y OrderItemModifier para gestionar modificadores y snapshot de selección.",
    "Creación de órdenes con validación completa (minSelect/maxSelect, stock, disponibilidad) y cálculo server-side de precios, con soporte para distintos tipos de orden (DINE_IN, TAKE_AWAY, DELIVERY) y número de mesa.",
    "Actualización rápida del estado de órdenes para display de cocina y atención, con nuevos estados PREPARING, READY, SERVED.",
    "Listados administrativos de órdenes con filtros por estado y detalle completo de usuario, items, modificadores y productos.",
    "Endpoints REST protegidos con JWT y roles, incluyendo seguridad en endpoints administrativos."
  ],
  "user_flow_summary": [
    "Administrador crea producto físico con grupos de modificadores anidados via POST /admin/products, con validaciones y creación de variants y modificadores.",
    "Administrador actualiza producto y sus modificadores con PUT /admin/products/:id que reemplaza grupos y opciones.",
    "Usuario crea orden via POST /orders indicando tipo, mesa, items con variantes y modificadores; backend valida reglas de selección y stock, calcula total y decrementa inventario.",
    "Administrador actualiza estado de orden via PATCH /admin/orders/:id/status para reflejar operaciones en cocina y atención.",
    "Administrador consulta listado de órdenes via GET /admin/orders con filtro opcional por estado y visualización detallada."
  ],
  "validation_criteria": [
    "La creación y actualización de productos debe validar la estructura y restricciones de modificadores y devolver errores HTTP 400 en caso de violaciones.",
    "La creación de órdenes debe validar la consistencia de cantidades, selección de modificadores según minSelect y maxSelect, disponibilidad de stock y existencia de variantes y modificadores; en caso de error debe retornar apropiados códigos 400 o 404.",
    "La actualización de estado de órdenes sólo debe ser accesible por usuarios con rol ADMIN y reflejar correctamente el nuevo estado; debe manejar casos donde la orden no existe con error 404.",
    "Los datos retornados en consultas administrativas deben incluir información completa de modificadores y usuarios ordenantes.",
    "El sistema debe soportar migraciones Prisma para los nuevos modelos y enums sin afectar datos existentes y garantizar compatibilidad ascendente."
  ],
  "code_summary": {
    "tech_stack": [
      "TypeScript",
      "NestJS",
      "Prisma ORM",
      "PostgreSQL",
      "Jest",
      "class-validator",
      "class-transformer",
      "JWT (Passport)",
      "Redis (cache-manager)"
    ],
    "features": [
      {
        "name": "Create Product with Modifier Groups",
        "description": "POST /admin/products - Creates a product with optional nested modifier groups (restaurant menu items). Each modifier group has name, minSelect, maxSelect and an array of modifiers with name, priceAdjustment, stock, isAvailable. Also creates a default ProductVariant. Requires ADMIN role JWT.",
        "files": [
          "src/modules/products/products.controller.ts",
          "src/modules/products/products.service.ts",
          "src/modules/products/dto/create-product.dto.ts",
          "src/modules/products/dto/create-modifier-group.dto.ts"
        ],
        "api_doc": {
          "openapi": "3.0.0",
          "paths": {
            "/admin/products": {
              "post": {
                "summary": "Create product with optional modifier groups",
                "security": [
                  {
                    "bearerAuth": []
                  }
                ],
                "requestBody": {
                  "required": true,
                  "content": {
                    "application/json": {
                      "schema": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "required": [
                          "name",
                          "slug",
                          "description",
                          "productType",
                          "basePrice",
                          "images"
                        ],
                        "properties": {
                          "name": {
                            "type": "string"
                          },
                          "slug": {
                            "type": "string"
                          },
                          "description": {
                            "type": "string"
                          },
                          "productType": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "enum": [
                              "DIGITAL",
                              "PHYSICAL",
                              "SERVICE"
                            ]
                          },
                          "basePrice": {
                            "type": "number"
                          },
                          "images": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "items": {
                              "type": "string"
                            }
                          },
                          "stock": {
                            "type": "integer"
                          },
                          "sku": {
                            "type": "string"
                          },
                          "published": {
                            "type": "boolean"
                          },
                          "modifierGroups": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "items": {
                              "type": "object",
                              "required": [
                                "name",
                                "modifiers"
                              ],
                              "properties": {
                                "name": {
                                  "type": "string"
                                },
                                "minSelect": {
                                  "type": "integer",
                                  "default": 0
                                },
                                "maxSelect": {
                                  "type": "integer",
                                  "default": 1
                                },
                                "modifiers": {
                                  "type": "array",
                                  "minItems": 1,
                                  "items": {
                                    "type": "object",
                                    "required": [
                                      "name"
                                    ],
                                    "properties": {
                                      "name": {
                                        "type": "string"
                                      },
                                      "priceAdjustment": {
                                        "type": "number",
                                        "default": 0
                                      },
                                      "stock": {
                                        "type": "integer"
                                      },
                                      "isAvailable": {
                                        "type": "boolean",
                                        "default": true
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "responses": {
                  "201": {
                    "description": "Product created with variants and modifier groups"
                  },
                  "400": {
                    "description": "Validation error or duplicate slug"
                  },
                  "401": {
                    "description": "Unauthorized"
                  },
                  "403": {
                    "description": "Forbidden - not ADMIN"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Update Product with Modifier Groups",
        "description": "PUT /admin/products/:id - Updates a product and replaces modifier groups (delete all + recreate). Requires ADMIN role JWT.",
        "files": [
          "src/modules/products/products.controller.ts",
          "src/modules/products/products.service.ts"
        ],
        "api_doc": {
          "openapi": "3.0.0",
          "paths": {
            "/admin/products/{id}": {
              "put": {
                "summary": "Update product with modifier groups (replace strategy)",
                "security": [
                  {
                    "bearerAuth": []
                  }
                ],
                "parameters": [
                  {
                    "name": "id",
                    "in": "path",
                    "required": true,
                    "schema": {
                      "type": "string"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "requestBody": {
                  "required": true,
                  "content": {
                    "application/json": {
                      "schema": {
                        "$ref": "#/components/schemas/CreateProductDto"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "responses": {
                  "200": {
                    "description": "Product updated"
                  },
                  "404": {
                    "description": "Product not found"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Create Order with Modifiers and Table",
        "description": "POST /orders - Creates an order with server-side price calculation. Accepts variantId, quantity, notes per item, and modifiers with quantity. Validates minSelect/maxSelect, modifier availability, stock. Uses atomic decrement for inventory. Supports OrderType (DINE_IN, TAKE_AWAY, DELIVERY) and tableNumber.",
        "files": [
          "src/modules/orders/orders.controller.ts",
          "src/modules/orders/orders.service.ts",
          "src/modules/orders/dto/create-order.dto.ts"
        ],
        "api_doc": {
          "openapi": "3.0.0",
          "paths": {
            "/orders": {
              "post": {
                "summary": "Create order with server-side price calculation",
                "security": [
                  {
                    "bearerAuth": []
                  }
                ],
                "requestBody": {
                  "required": true,
                  "content": {
                    "application/json": {
                      "schema": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "required": [
                          "items"
                        ],
                        "properties": {
                          "orderType": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "enum": [
                              "DINE_IN",
                              "TAKE_AWAY",
                              "DELIVERY"
                            ],
                            "default": "DINE_IN"
                          },
                          "tableNumber": {
                            "type": "string"
                          },
                          "items": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "minItems": 1,
                            "items": {
                              "type": "object",
                              "required": [
                                "variantId",
                                "quantity"
                              ],
                              "properties": {
                                "variantId": {
                                  "type": "string"
                                },
                                "quantity": {
                                  "type": "integer",
                                  "minimum": 1
                                },
                                "notes": {
                                  "type": "string"
                                },
                                "modifiers": {
                                  "type": "array",
                                  "items": {
                                    "type": "object",
                                    "required": [
                                      "modifierId",
                                      "quantity"
                                    ],
                                    "properties": {
                                      "modifierId": {
                                        "type": "string"
                                      },
                                      "quantity": {
                                        "type": "integer",
                                        "minimum": 1
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "responses": {
                  "201": {
                    "description": "Order created with calculated total"
                  },
                  "400": {
                    "description": "Validation error, stock insufficient, or modifier constraints violated"
                  },
                  "404": {
                    "description": "Variant or modifier not found"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Update Order Status (Kitchen Display)",
        "description": "PATCH /admin/orders/:id/status - Quick status change for kitchen display or waiter. Supports: PENDING, APPROVED, PROCESSING, PREPARING, READY, SERVED, SHIPPED, DELIVERED, CANCELLED, REFUNDED. Requires ADMIN role.",
        "files": [
          "src/modules/orders/orders.controller.ts",
          "src/modules/orders/orders.service.ts",
          "src/modules/orders/dto/update-order-status.dto.ts"
        ],
        "api_doc": {
          "openapi": "3.0.0",
          "paths": {
            "/admin/orders/{id}/status": {
              "patch": {
                "summary": "Update order status for kitchen display",
                "security": [
                  {
                    "bearerAuth": []
                  }
                ],
                "parameters": [
                  {
                    "name": "id",
                    "in": "path",
                    "required": true,
                    "schema": {
                      "type": "string"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "requestBody": {
                  "required": true,
                  "content": {
                    "application/json": {
                      "schema": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "required": [
                          "status"
                        ],
                        "properties": {
                          "status": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "enum": [
                              "PENDING",
                              "APPROVED",
                              "PROCESSING",
                              "PREPARING",
                              "READY",
                              "SERVED",
                              "SHIPPED",
                              "DELIVERED",
                              "CANCELLED",
                              "REFUNDED"
                            ]
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "responses": {
                  "200": {
                    "description": "Order status updated"
                  },
                  "404": {
                    "description": "Order not found"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "List Admin Orders",
        "description": "GET /admin/orders?status=... - Lists all orders with optional status filter. Includes user info, items with modifiers, and product details. Requires ADMIN role.",
        "files": [
          "src/modules/orders/orders.controller.ts",
          "src/modules/orders/orders.service.ts"
        ],
        "api_doc": {
          "openapi": "3.0.0",
          "paths": {
            "/admin/orders": {
              "get": {
                "summary": "List all orders with optional status filter",
                "security": [
                  {
                    "bearerAuth": []
                  }
                ],
                "parameters": [
                  {
                    "name": "status",
                    "in": "query",
                    "required": false,
                    "schema": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "PENDING",
                        "APPROVED",
                        "PROCESSING",
                        "PREPARING",
                        "READY",
                        "SERVED",
                        "SHIPPED",
                        "DELIVERED",
                        "CANCELLED",
                        "REFUNDED"
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "responses": {
                  "200": {
                    "description": "List of orders with items, modifiers, and user info"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
